column5: Hi all, Managing to grab short sessions early and late recently. I got out just before sunrise last week, stunning scenery and a few fish, great start to the day.
Cool video. Been a few years since I did any ice fishing. God, just looks so cold though.

IMO, the catch if it happens , is a bonus. Watching a new day start like that, is the best start of a day.
